IMAPStore rafael.palomar@ntnu.no-remote
Host outlook.office365.com
Port 993
User rafael.palomar@ntnu.no
PassCmd "mutt_oauth2.py ~/.password-store/email/ntnu.no.gpg"
AuthMechs XOAUTH2
TLSType IMAPS
CertificateFile /etc/ssl/certs/ca-certificates.crt

MaildirStore rafael.palomar@ntnu.no-local
Subfolders Verbatim
Path /home/rafael/.local/share/mail/rafael.palomar@ntnu.no/
Inbox /home/rafael/.local/share/mail/rafael.palomar@ntnu.no/INBOX

Channel rafael.palomar@ntnu.no
Expunge Both
Far :rafael.palomar@ntnu.no-remote:
Near :rafael.palomar@ntnu.no-local:
Patterns * !"[Gmail]/All Mail"
Create Both
SyncState *
MaxMessages 0
ExpireUnread no
# End profile


